---
title: Creole Chicken & Roast Veggie Couscous with Toasted Almonds & Garlic Dip
description: Creole spices, brown sugar and lemon combine to give chicken an irresistible flavour boost. Perched on a bed of
tender roast veggies and fluffy couscous, then topped with a garlicky sauce, this has something for everyone.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
